<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Controle | Netflix</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>

    <main>

        <div class="text-center mt-5" style="width: 100%; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
            <img src="/img/undraw_wallet_aym5.svg" alt="pagamento" style="width: 100%; max-width: 400px;">

            <h4 class="mt-5">Vencimento de acesso!</h4>
            <h2>
                <%= date.day %> de <strong>
                        <%= date.month %>
                    </strong> de <%= date.year %>
            </h2>

            <p>
                Olá
                <strong>
                    <%= user.name %>
                </strong>, tudo bem? Seu acesso a <strong>Netflix</strong>
                expirou, faça o pix no valor de <strong>
                    R$ <%= user.value %>
                </strong> equivalente ao seu plano para continuar sua diversão.
                <br>
                Abraço!
            </p>
            <div class="d-grid">
                <button class="btn btn-danger">073.790.423-27</button>
                <small class="mt-2">CPF é a chave PIX</small>
            </div>

        </div>

    </main>

</body>

</html>